Examples

data("bike_score")

banister_model <- dorem(
  Test_5min_Power ~ BikeScore,
  bike_score,
  method = "banister",
  control = dorem_control(
        cv_folds = 3,
        cv_repeats = 5,
        shuffle = TRUE
  )
)
